    "chunk_text": "A tragic railway accident occurred on the morning of 09.06.2026 at the Halpe railway crossing within the Kandana Police Division when a train travelling from Chilaw to Colombo Fort collided with a three-wheeler attempting to cross the railway track.\n\nThe driver of the three-wheeler and a female passenger travelling in the rear seat sustained fatal injuries and died as a result of the collision.\n\nPreliminary investigations have disclosed that the three-wheeler had proceeded across the railway crossing despite the warning bell and signal lights being activated to indicate the approaching train.\n\nThe bodies are due to be forwarded to the Ragama Hospital for post-mortem examinations.\n\nFurther investigations into the incident are being carried out by the Kandana Police.\n\nPolice Media Division."
